President Obama welcomes the announcement by King Hamad bin Isa al-Khalifa of Bahrain regarding important changes to the cabinet and his commitment to reform. The United States supports the national dialogue initiative led by Crown Prince Salman bin Hamad al-Khalifa and encourages a process that is inclusive, non-sectarian, and responsive to the people of Bahrain. The dialogue provides an opportunity for meaningful reform and for all Bahrainis to work together towards a more just future. The United States believes that Bahrain's stability will be improved by respecting the universal rights of its people and implementing reforms that meet the aspirations of all Bahrainis.